Package edu.umn.biomedicus.uima.rtf

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdaptedPropertyCasMapping
    Created by benknoll on 7/13/15.
    CasMappings
    Mappings from RTF elements to UIMA CAS elements. Is a POJO/bean that is XML-serializable via JAXB.
    ControlWordCasMapping
    XML bean object for a mapping from a RTF control word to a UIMA annotation. When the control word is encountered, the annotation is emitted in the output destination view.
    DestinationCasMapping
    A mapping from an rtf destination name to an UIMA view name. Controls what rtf destinations output to uima views.
    IgnoreOutputDestination  
    ParagraphAnnotator
    Annotates paragraphs in rtf text using annotations for the \par keyword.
    PropertyCasMapping
    A mapping from some kind of rtf property state to an annotation type for emission in UIMA.
    PropertyCasMappingAdapter
    XML adapter for PropertyCasMapping.
    RtfParserAnnotator
    Annotator which parses rtf documents.
    TableAnnotator
    Annotates table elements from rtf text using the row/cell/nestedcell/nestedrow end annotations.
